msgid "Tuist Pro includes support through our community forum and GitHub issues. Enterprise plans include dedicated support via Slack channels with high priority response times."
msgstr "Tuist Pro 包含透過社群論壇與 GitHub 問題的支援。企業方案包含透過 Slack 頻道提供專屬支援並享有高優先回應時間。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/about.html.heex:12
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Tuist bridges the gaps in Apple's tooling that prevent teams from moving fast. We solve the build complexity, workflow friction, and collaboration challenges—so you can deliver exceptional apps at speed."
msgstr "Tuist 彌補 Apple 工具的不足，讓團隊得以快速前進。我們解決建置複雜度、流程摩擦與協作挑戰，讓您能迅速交付卓越應用。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_controller.ex:220
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Tuist has allowed us to migrate our existing monolythic codebase to a modular one. We extracted our different domains into specific modules. It allowed us to remove extra dependencies, ease testability and made our development cycles faster than ever. It even allowed us to bring up 'Test Apps' for speeding up our development on each module."
msgstr "Tuist 使我們能將既有單體碼庫遷移為模組化。我們將不同領域抽離為專屬模組，移除額外相依性、簡化測試並使開發循環更快。它甚至讓我們建立「測試應用」以加速各模組開發。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_controller.ex:154
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Tuist has been a game-changer for our large codebase, where multiple engineers collaborate simultaneously. I've been using it since version 1, and it's been incredible to see how the product has evolved and expanded with new features over time."
msgstr "Tuist 對我們的大型碼庫帶來革新，多位工程師可同步協作。我從 1.0 版本開始使用，見證產品隨時間演進、功能不斷擴充，令人難以置信。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_controller.ex:169
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Tuist has revolutionized our iOS development workflow at DraftKings. Its automation capabilities have streamlined project generation, build settings, and dependency management. Highly recommended for iOS teams seeking workflow optimization."
msgstr "Tuist 徹底改變了 DraftKings 的 iOS 開發流程。其自動化功能簡化了專案產生、建置設定及相依管理。非常推薦尋求流程優化的 iOS 團隊使用。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/structured_markup.ex:99
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Tuist is designed to grow with you. Only add a card if you need more than the free tier limits or dedicated support."
msgstr "Tuist 設計為伴隨您共同成長。只有當超出免費階層限制或需要專屬支援時才需新增方案方案。"

